data.Name: Cosmo Thundercat
data.Bio: Music born in Adelaide, AU. Garage-folk rhythms, with a raw and honest personality. Recently supporting the likes of Augie March, Thirsty Merc, The Snowdroppers, Goodbyemotel (USA) and hosting a series of bustling headline shows, Cosmo Thundercat have garnered attention from local and national Australian radio, receiving uplifting reviews. The band are currently recording new material set for release mid-2016. Read more on Last.fm
